@node BugReports " Send bugreports to... "
@toc Main

 In case you discover any bugs in the program or this AmigaGuide document,
 please let me know.

 Please make the bug-description as well documented as possible. This will
 make it easier for me to locate the bug. Let me know what kind of system
 you use and what programs you run in the background.
 Also try to make the bug reappear under the same conditions, it might have
 been something else that caused the problem (like coffee in the keyboard,
 if this is the case, don't bother to make the bug reappear).

 My address is:

  Johan Stenarson
  Björnstigen 17
  S-646 00 GNESTA
  SWEDEN

@endnode
